# 🍰 Tarie Cakes - Handcrafted Luxury Cakes

[![React](https://img.shields.io/badge/React-18.3.1-blue.svg)](https://reactjs.org/)
[![TypeScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/TypeScript-5.6.2-blue.svg)](https://www.typescriptlang.org/)
[![Chakra UI](https://img.shields.io/badge/Chakra_UI-2.8.2-teal.svg)](https://chakra-ui.com/)
[![Vite](https://img.shields.io/badge/Vite-6.0.5-purple.svg)](https://vitejs.dev/)

> *Where passion meets perfection in every decadent bite*

Welcome to **Tarie Cakes**, a stunning e-commerce platform for Mutare, Zimbabwe's premier luxury cake boutique. This beautifully crafted React application showcases handcrafted cakes that transform ordinary moments into extraordinary celebrations.

![Tarie Cakes Hero](src/assets/images/tarie-cakes-hero.jpg)

## ✨ Features

### 🎨 **Elegant Design System**
- **Velvet Noir Theme**: Deep burgundy, warm cream, and antique gold color palette
- **Responsive Design**: Flawless experience across all devices
- **Smooth Animations**: Powered by Framer Motion for delightful interactions
- **Glass Morphism**: Modern UI with backdrop blur effects

### 🛒 **E-Commerce Functionality**
- **Interactive Menu**: Browse our extensive cake collection with detailed descriptions
- **Smart Cart System**: Add, remove, and manage items with persistent state
- **Real-time Pricing**: Dynamic calculations with Zimbabwe dollar pricing
- **WhatsApp Integration**: Direct ordering through WhatsApp for instant communication

### 📱 **User Experience**
- **Client-side Routing**: Fast navigation with React Router v6
- **Image Gallery**: Stunning cake photography with lightbox functionality
- **Contact Integration**: Embedded Google Maps and contact forms
- **Newsletter Signup**: Stay connected with sweet updates

### 🎯 **Performance Optimized**
- **Lazy Loading**: Components load on demand for faster initial page loads
- **Image Optimization**: Efficient asset handling with Vite
- **TypeScript**: Type-safe development for reliability
- **Modern Build Tools**: Lightning-fast development and production builds

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend Framework
- **React 18** - Modern React with concurrent features
- **TypeScript** - Type-safe JavaScript for robust development
- **Vite** - Next-generation frontend tooling

### UI & Styling
- **Chakra UI** - Component library with accessibility first
- **Framer Motion** - Production-ready motion library
- **Emotion** - CSS-in-JS styling solution

### Routing & State
- **React Router v6** - Declarative routing for React
- **React Context** - State management for cart functionality

### Development Tools
- **ESLint** - Code linting and formatting
- **Prettier** - Code formatting (via ESLint)
- **Vite Plugin React** - Fast React development

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+ and npm
- Git

### Installation

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/tarie-cakes.git
   cd tarie-cakes
   ```

2. **Install dependencies**
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

3. **Start development server**
   ```bash
   npm run dev
   ```

4. **Open your browser**
   Navigate to `http://localhost:5174`

### Build for Production

```bash
npm run build
```

### Preview Production Build

```bash
npm run preview
```

